i=4: array[4]=2, array[3]=6: 2<6 -> swap -> {5,3,4,2,6,1}? No: after forward pass array={5,3,4,6,2,1}
i=4: array[4]=2, array[3]=6: 2<6 -> swap -> {5,3,4,2,6,1}
i=3: array[3]=2, array[2]=4: 2<4 -> swap -> {5,3,2,4,6,1}
i=2: array[2]=2, array[1]=3: 2<3 -> swap -> {5,2,3,4,6,1}
i=1: array[1]=2, array[0]=5: 2<5 -> swap -> {2,5,3,4,6,1}? This doesn't look right.
