questions.question:
Consider the following C program:

#include <stdio.h>
int jumble(int x, int y) {
    x = 2*x + y;
    return x;
}
int main() {
    int x = 2, y = 5;
    y = jumble(y, x);
    x = jumble(y, x);
    printf("%d \n", x);
    return 0;
}

The value printed by the program is __________.
